Sorry, I spoke in haste here.  Although the smaller MSS is unfortunate, I didn't think through the numbers thoroughly enough and it's probably not true that's the main cause of the problems at the bandwidths seen here.  @sbrivio-rh's `SO_RCVLOWAT` prototypes are showing promising results, and it's also possible there's something else going on here that's not yet apparent.

